        <div class="wwf-phs-border ">
          <h1>PHILANTHROPY &amp; FOUNDATION GIFTS</h1>
          <p><p><strong>Creating a better future for our planet</strong></p>

<p><span><span><strong><span><span><span>Thank you for your interest in WWF. We rely on generous supporters like you to invest in our global work and help us secure a world where both people and nature thrive. Each philanthropic contribution we receive supports lasting conservation solutions that will benefit species, people and the environment.</span></span></span></strong> </span></span></p></p>


          

